00:26:29.280 --> 00:26:31.830
And I thought, in
my mind, it was

00:26:31.830 --> 00:26:33.870
a completely trivial question.

00:26:33.870 --> 00:26:35.550
So I made a few
drawings on the board

00:26:35.550 --> 00:26:37.480
