00:33:10.150 --> 00:33:11.620
ERIC MAZUR: So what happens
when something melts?

00:33:11.620 --> 00:33:12.777
Very good question.

00:33:12.777 --> 00:33:14.360
Again, we only deal
with solids, so we

00:33:14.360 --> 00:33:17.200
