00:33:17.200 --> 00:33:18.870
But as it gets
hotter and hotter,

00:33:18.870 --> 00:33:21.370
the atoms go further and
further away from each other.

00:33:21.370 --> 00:33:24.400
At a certain point they
lose their attraction

00:33:24.400 --> 00:33:26.310
and they lose their
position, and they melt.

00:33:26.310 --> 00:33:30.260
They go into a different
phase, and they eventually

00:33:30.260 --> 00:33:32.260
become a gas.

00:33:32.260 --> 00:33:35.760
But we won't get
