00:33:47.300 --> 00:33:49.640
And if you heat it
up again, it expands.

00:33:49.640 --> 00:33:51.950
Until the melting point,
when strange things happen.

00:33:51.950 --> 00:33:54.060
But yeah, it's true
for all solids.

00:33:54.060 --> 00:33:55.710
All hard solids.

00:33:55.710 --> 00:33:58.900
A bagel, or a fried egg.

00:33:58.900 --> 00:34:01.521
It won't be, but any hard solid.

