need later in life.

00:52:26.620 --> 00:52:29.040
It's the skills, really,
that matter, right?

00:52:29.040 --> 00:52:31.820
In the traditional approach to
teaching you start by thinking,

00:52:31.820 --> 00:52:33.784
what am I going to
cover in this course?

00:52:33.784 --> 00:52:35.700
Topic one, topic two,
topic three, topic four.

00:52:35.700 --> 00:52:37.839
Then you start covering
in the classroom and then

00:52:37.839 --> 00:52:39.380
after a month or so
