distracted with cartoons,

00:56:13.900 --> 00:56:15.690
and we polled them again.

00:56:15.690 --> 00:56:19.960
And then we took another set
of students and we polled them,

00:56:19.960 --> 00:56:22.420
and then we were silent
for two minutes so

00:56:22.420 --> 00:56:26.450
that they don't exchange
ideas and they don't talk.

00:56:26.450 --> 00:56:29.150
