01:04:15.451 --> 01:04:18.420
I think it was Dan Pink who once
said that the single strongest

01:04:18.420 --> 01:04:22.580
indicator of success is
persistence and perseverance.

01:04:22.580 --> 01:04:24.700
I think it was he
who once said that.

01:04:24.700 --> 01:04:27.880
And I think that's so true.

01:04:27.880 --> 01:04:30.380
If you stick to it,
if you push yourself.

01:04:30.380 --> 01:04:32.280
Take the light bulb.

01:04:32.280 --> 01:04:33.210
Thomas Edison.

01:04:33.210 --> 01:04:34.220
He didn't just
invent a light bulb.

01:04:34.220 --> 01:04:36.465
