before he finally got there.

01:04:36.465 --> 01:04:39.080
But he persisted and
continued and continued.

01:04:39.080 --> 01:04:42.260
Failure is so essential
and we don't teach failure.

01:04:42.260 --> 01:04:44.440
Failure means you
take points off.

01:04:44.440 --> 01:04:46.410
And that brings
