01:04:50.920 --> 01:04:55.810
But assessment is actually
the other part of education.

01:04:55.810 --> 01:04:59.210
And I realized two years
ago, all of sudden,

01:04:59.210 --> 01:05:01.310
that the students
in my class were not

01:05:01.310 --> 01:05:02.850
really learning to learn.

01:05:02.850 --> 01:05:05.690
They were learning to
pass the assessment.

01:05:05.690 --> 01:05:08.070
And, of course,
in an ideal world

01:05:08.070 --> 01:05:09.572
those two things are the same.

01:05:09.572 --> 01:05:12.030
But the there are many shortcuts
to passing the assessment.

01:05:12.030 --> 01:05:13.640
It's not really learning.

01:05:13.640 --> 01:05:17.580
And that made me aware of the
fact that I really had to start

01:05:17.580 --> 01:05:20.660
radically changing
the assessment.

01:05:20.660 --> 01:05:23.400
Unfortunately, I think
