01:05:27.690 --> 01:05:30.180
Killer of Learning."

01:05:30.180 --> 01:05:34.120
Kind of a negative title,
but I truly believe.

01:05:34.120 --> 01:05:37.200
I spent all these years
thinking about the input.

01:05:37.200 --> 01:05:39.310
What do you do in the classroom?

01:05:39.310 --> 01:05:42.000
Not really thinking
about how the assessment

01:05:42.000 --> 01:05:44.640
is what drives the
students' study habits.

01:05:44.640 --> 01:05:49.520
So we need to spend as much time
rethinking the assessment as we

01:05:49.520 --> 01:05:51.990
are rethinking the
approach teaching.

01:05:51.990 --> 01:05:53.460
Much less work has
been done there,

01:05:53.460 --> 01:05:55.820
but there are some
promising approaches.

01:05:55.820 --> 01:05:58.980
KARA MILLER: Let me just
