Well, actually, they
said, our good students

01:06:30.650 --> 01:06:32.570
don't do well on your questions.

01:06:32.570 --> 01:06:34.550
Because the good students
did well on questions

01:06:34.550 --> 01:06:38.100
that are actually
quite meaningless.

01:06:38.100 --> 01:06:42.300
For five years I tried to change
the AP Physics B and C exam,

01:06:42.300 --> 01:06:46.590
only to realize that
ETS and the whole AP

01:06:46.590 --> 01:06:48.200
and standardized
testing enterprise

01:06:48.200 --> 01:06:51.470
is like a supertanker, which
is already hard to maneuver,

01:06:51.470 --> 01:06:52.840
where you've removed the rudder.

01:06:52.840 --> 01:06:54.140
There's only one way it can go.

01:06:54.140 --> 01:06:55.730
Straight.

01:06:55.730 --> 01:06:59.000
So it's unfortunate
