01:07:08.060 --> 01:07:11.480
And unfortunately, if you look
at the thinking skills that

01:07:11.480 --> 01:07:14.664
are tested by many
standardized instruments,

01:07:14.664 --> 01:07:15.580
they're not very high.

01:07:15.580 --> 01:07:19.300
A lot of them are remembering
and understanding, rather than

01:07:19.300 --> 01:07:24.045
being able to apply or analysis,
or any type of creative skill.

